snippet.title: Raptors in the Kitchen, Indie Horror Game Clip
snippet.description:
OUT NOW ON STEAM https://store.steampowered.com/app/1597040/Fossilfuel/?beta=0
A clip from the indie game Fossilfuel.
Fossilfuel is a horror game where the player has to sneak around horrific sharped toothed dinos that will use keen AI, sight, and sound to hunt the player. Take a look at the steam store below:

Steamstore
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1597040/Fossilfuel/?beta=0

Join the discord! https://discord.gg/K9hUQcnngb
